data.description: Perfect opportunity to own this diamond in the rough. The main home boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, offering amazing views, a custom back deck, and a patio area. Additionally, there is a secondary unit with a bathroom that was previously used as the seller's workshop and is in need of repairs, but it still holds huge potential for the right buyer. The added goat corral and greenhouse provide a great added touch to this property. The home is perched on top of the mountain, and below, you'll find a secondary entrance to a well and the potential use of the almost full 2 acres that come with the property. This is a must-see to truly appreciate this unique opportunity.
